    • getAllVeinMineableBlocks

      @NotNull public @NotNull BlockList getAllVeinMineableBlocks()
      Get a BlockList of all veinmineable blocks. The returned blocklist will contain unique block-state combinations from all categories and the global blocklist. Any changes made to the returned block list will not affect the underlying blocklist, therefore if any changes are required, they should be done to those returned by ToolCategory.getBlocklist() or getBlockListGlobal()
      Returns:
      get all veinmineable blocks
      See Also:
      ToolCategory.getBlocklist(), getBlockListGlobal()
